Zaldivar-Riveron et al. 2008
: 329 (included in subgenus Aleiodes Wesmael, 1838). Type species (by monotypy): Neorhogas luteus Szepligeti , 1906 [examined; = Aleiodes praetor (Reinhard, 1863)].

Chelonorhogas Enderlein, [Sept. 1st] 1912a: 258; Shenefelt 1975 : 1187; van Achterberg 1991 : 24 (as subgenus of Aleiodes Wesmael, 1838);
Zaldivar-Riveron et al. 2008
: 329 (as subgenus of Aleiodes Wesmael, 1838). Type species (by monotypy): Chelonorhogas rufithorax Enderlein, 1912 [examined; not Aleiodes rufithorax (Cameron, 1911) = A. convexus van Achterberg, 1991].

Eucystomastax Brues, [(end of?) Sept.] 1912: 223; Shaw 1993 : 5 (as subgenus of Aleiodes Wesmael, 1838);
Zaldivar-Riveron et al. 2004
